    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/nagaraja-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is offset by the high relevance of validation activities, multi-laboratory experimental confirmation across N=11 constructs, and all QoI comparison metrics well within acceptance bounds. Overall credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission at Medium assurance level. Note: the mesh convergence verification activity (https://uofa.net/synth/activity/mesh-convergence-study-noncannulated) was conducted as part of the discretization error assessment; associated convergence plots and GCI tabulations are referenced in the simulation plan but have not been formally linked as evidence artifacts in this package.",
